{
  "name": "au-token-domain-keywords",
  "description": "Per pre-registration §M5. Keyword sets that map a finding's `domain` field to one of the 11 au-token work-package sub-topics. A finding belongs to a sub-topic if any keyword in its set is a substring match (case-insensitive) of the finding's `domain` field. Frozen before SEA2's first comparison dispatch (commit reference in `docs/comparison-protocol.md` §6).",
